<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62c38851-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s3666"><num value="3666">§ 3666.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of carrying out the activities under this subchapter, there are authorized to be appropriated such sums as are necessary for fiscal years 2011 through 2015.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62c38852-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/559/tI/s107">Pub. L. 106–559, title I, § 107</ref>, formerly § 106, <date date="2000-12-21">Dec. 21, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/2781">114 Stat. 2781</ref>; renumbered § 107 and amended <ref href="/us/pl/111/211/tII">Pub. L. 111–211, title II</ref>, §§ 214(a)(2)(A), 242(b)(3)(A), <date date="2010-07-29">July 29, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/2270">124 Stat. 2270</ref>, 2292.)</sourceCredit>
